@glindex data declaration 

Also, a special kind of data predicates exists, 
@coindex concurrent predicates
@glindex concurrent predicates
@emph{concurrent predicates}, which can be used to communicate/synchronize among different execution threads (see @ref{Low-level concurrency/multithreading primitives}). 

Data predicates must be declared through a 
@glindex data/1
@code{data/1} declaration. Concurrent data predicates must be declared through a 
